{"lang": "zh_TW", "eventid": "main_15", "eventName": "解離重組", "entryType": "MAINLINE", "storyCode": "15-12", "avgTag": "行動前", "storyName": "目擊眾神死亡的荒原", "storyInfo": "普瑞賽斯引導卡特斯感染者去見證被她儲存在源石內部的資料，這些資料是普瑞賽斯曾見證的過去，也揭開了毀滅文明的危機的一角。\n", "storyList": [{"id": 0, "prop": "HEADER", "attributes": {"key": "title_test", "is_skippable": "true", "fit_mode": "BLACK_MASK"}}, {"id": 1, "prop": "stopmusic", "attributes": {}}, {"id": 2, "prop": "dialog", "attributes": {}}, {"id": 3, "prop": "Blocker", "attributes": {"a": 0.0, "r": 0.0, "g": 0.0, "b": 0.0, "fadetime": 0.0, "block": "true"}}, {"id": 4, "prop": "Blocker", "attributes": {"a": 1.0, "r": 0.0, "g": 0.0, "b": 0.0, "fadetime": 2.0, "block": "true"}}, {"id": 5, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {}}, {"id": 6, "prop": "PlayMusic", "attributes": {"intro": "$loneliness_intro", "key": "$loneliness_loop", "volume": 0.6}}, {"id": 7, "prop": "Image", "attributes": {"image": "60_i09", "screenadapt": "coverall", "xScale": 1.4, "yScale": 1.4}}, {"id": 8, "prop": "ImageTween", "attributes": {"yTo": 0.0, "duration": 60.0, "block": "false"}}, {"id": 9, "prop": "Blocker", "attributes": {"a": 0.0, "r": 0.0, "g": 0.0, "b": 0.0, "fadetime": 4.0, "block": "true"}}, {"id": 10, "prop": "Delay", "attributes": {"time": 1.0}}, {"id": 11, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "我們審視並解讀我們文明的前世今生，如僧侶祈求神諭。"}}, {"id": 12, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "談及預言文明可能步向的未來，人類又何嘗不是甘之如飴？"}}, {"id": 13, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "起初，我們揮舞著手中那僅有的、可憐的片面真理去與“神明”對話。"}}, {"id": 14, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "但回應我們的，卻是緘默不語。"}}, {"id": 15, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "於是，我們轉而開始觀察，觀察我們同類的命運——"}}, {"id": 16, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "那些落後於我們的，或是略微領先於我們的……最終我們得知“自然造物終有一死”。"}}, {"id": 17, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "於是人類由此推斷，這就是神明從未言說的神諭。"}}, {"id": 18, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "轉眼間，我們自認晉升為了掌握宇宙真理的哲人。", "name": "溫柔的聲音"}}, {"id": 19, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "我們一邊小心翼翼地“壟斷”這由犧牲所換來的神諭，一邊用所謂的樂觀去宣揚終將到來的毀滅。", "name": "溫柔的聲音"}}, {"id": 20, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "“自然造物終有一死，我們能做的，唯有在毀滅之前留下真理。”", "name": "溫柔的聲音"}}, {"id": 21, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "你在那艘船上生活了一段時間，也認識了一些可愛的生命。那你同意這種看法嗎？", "name": "溫柔的聲音"}}, {"id": 22, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "……您並不同意幽靈他們的看法？", "name": "希爾達"}}, {"id": 23, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "我敬重他們。", "name": "溫柔的聲音"}}, {"id": 24, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "他們是偉大的人，但他們中的絕大部分人也只是稍稍聰明一點的愚人。", "name": "溫柔的聲音"}}, {"id": 25, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "您為什麼要問我這個問題？還有……為什麼您要帶我來這裡？", "name": "希爾達"}}, {"id": 26, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "我記得，明明剛才我們還在那個走廊。", "name": "希爾達"}}, {"id": 27, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "這裡與那裡都沒有區別。", "name": "溫柔的聲音"}}, {"id": 28, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "你心裡有太多的困惑，而這裡能夠解答你的問題。", "name": "溫柔的聲音"}}, {"id": 29, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "這裡到底是什麼地方？", "name": "希爾達"}}, {"id": 30, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "銘記文明死去的墓地。", "name": "溫柔的聲音"}}, {"id": 31, "prop": "dialog", "attributes": {}}, {"id": 32, "prop": "PlaySound", "attributes": {"key": "$d_avg_scifiwave", "volume": 0.6}}, {"id": 33, "prop": "Image", "attributes": {"image": "60_i09", "screenadapt": "coverall", "xScale": 1.05, "yScale": 1.05, "fadetime": 2.0}}, {"id": 34, "prop": "ImageTween", "attributes": {"xScaleFrom": 1.05, "yScaleFrom": 1.05, "xScaleTo": 1.0, "yScaleTo": 1.0, "duration": 20.0, "block": "false"}}, {"id": 35, "prop": "Delay", "attributes": {"time": 2.0}}, {"id": 36, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "卡特斯無法看出材質的巨大雕像聳立於大地之上。"}}, {"id": 37, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "環形的波紋層層散開，向上觸及陰雲遮擋的蒼穹之外，向下沉積在灰白色的土地上。"}}, {"id": 38, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "文明誕生於那片浩瀚的宇宙，就如同一滴雨水墜入大海，勢必蕩起漣漪，在宇宙中留下自己的痕跡。", "name": "溫柔的聲音"}}, {"id": 39, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "他們交流，他們仇恨，他們相愛，最終他們也會死去。", "name": "溫柔的聲音"}}, {"id": 40, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "死去文明的漣漪永恆地凝固在這墓碑之上。而那些璀璨如明星，啟迪無數後來者的先行者哪怕已經在時光中消逝——", "name": "溫柔的聲音"}}, {"id": 41, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "他們依舊會對宇宙產生無可比擬的影響。你看，他們蕩起的漣漪形成了我們所站立的這片大地。", "name": "溫柔的聲音"}}, {"id": 42, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "而他們的遺產供養著新生者，也承接著新生的文明在宇宙中留下的足跡。", "name": "溫柔的聲音"}}, {"id": 43, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "但它好像……斷裂了？就、就像一截斷掉的樹樁。", "name": "希爾達"}}, {"id": 44, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "你不是第一個這樣形容它的人。", "name": "溫柔的聲音"}}, {"id": 45, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "有一位於我而言很重要的人也曾向我這樣說起過。", "name": "溫柔的聲音"}}, {"id": 46, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "一個絕對存在的終極孜孜不倦地收割著這可憐樹樁上新發出的枝椏，而我們卻對祂一無所知。", "name": "溫柔的聲音"}}, {"id": 47, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "您向我展示的一切就像……神蹟……", "name": "希爾達"}}, {"id": 48, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "您救了我，從崩解中……救了我……", "name": "希爾達"}}, {"id": 49, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "……神明。", "name": "希爾達"}}, {"id": 50, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "“神明”？", "name": "溫柔的聲音"}}, {"id": 51, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "我只是一個希望解釋宇宙的語言學家。", "name": "溫柔的聲音"}}, {"id": 52, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "我的名字是普瑞賽斯。", "name": "溫柔的聲音"}}, {"id": 53, "prop": "dialog", "attributes": {}}, {"id": 54, "prop": "Blocker", "attributes": {"a": 0.0, "r": 0.0, "g": 0.0, "b": 0.0, "fadetime": 0.0, "block": "true"}}, {"id": 55, "prop": "Blocker", "attributes": {"a": 1.0, "r": 0.0, "g": 0.0, "b": 0.0, "fadetime": 2.0, "block": "true"}}, {"id": 56, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {}}, {"id": 57, "prop": "image", "attributes": {}}, {"id": 58, "prop": "Background", "attributes": {"image": "60_g3_cvilizationtombstone", "screenadapt": "coverall"}}, {"id": 59, "prop": "Delay", "attributes": {"time": 1.0}}, {"id": 60, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "r", "name": "avg_npc_1719_1#1$1"}}, {"id": 61, "prop": "Blocker", "attributes": {"a": 0.0, "r": 0.0, "g": 0.0, "b": 0.0, "fadetime": 2.0, "block": "true"}}, {"id": 62, "prop": "Delay", "attributes": {"time": 1.0}}, {"id": 63, "prop": "PlaySound", "attributes": {"key": "$d_avg_universe_fts", "volume": 1.0, "loop": "true", "channel": "u"}}, {"id": 64, "prop": "StopSound", "attributes": {"channel": "u", "fadetime": 3.0}}, {"id": 65, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "l", "name": "avg_npc_1718_1#1$1", "duration": 1.5}}, {"id": 66, "prop": "Delay", "attributes": {"time": 2.0}}, {"id": 67, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "l", "name": "avg_npc_1718_1#1$1", "focus": "l"}}, {"id": 68, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "嚴格來說，我並沒有救下你。", "name": "普瑞賽斯"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_1718_1#1$1"}, {"id": 69, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "r", "name": "avg_npc_1719_1#9$1", "focus": "r"}}, {"id": 70, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "——？！", "name": "希爾達"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_1719_1#9$1"}, {"id": 71, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "l", "name": "avg_npc_1718_1#1$1", "focus": "l"}}, {"id": 72, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "你的死亡的確已經發生，物質向資訊轉譯的過程我並未干預。", "name": "普瑞賽斯"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_1718_1#1$1"}, {"id": 73, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "但物質的消亡並不意味著真正的死亡，資訊不會被輕易泯滅。源石記錄了你的資料。", "name": "普瑞賽斯"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_1718_1#1$1"}, {"id": 74, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "r", "name": "avg_npc_1719_1#9$1", "focus": "r"}}, {"id": 75, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "……但、但我還能思考。在那艘艦船上，我確切地感受到了我在生活，還有那些鮮活的——", "name": "希爾達"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_1719_1#9$1"}, {"id": 76, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "l", "name": "avg_npc_1718_1#1$1", "focus": "l"}}, {"id": 77, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "那同樣只是一段無限重複的資料流而已。", "name": "普瑞賽斯"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_1718_1#1$1"}, {"id": 78, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "我特意留下了一些歷史碎片來觀察我們過去的生活。", "name": "普瑞賽斯"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_1718_1#1$1"}, {"id": 79, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "r", "name": "avg_npc_1719_1#1$1", "focus": "r"}}, {"id": 80, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "所以，就像一場夢境？", "name": "希爾達"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_1719_1#1$1"}, {"id": 81, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "l", "name": "avg_npc_1718_1#1$1", "focus": "l"}}, {"id": 82, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "夢是籠統且主觀的描述，在你觸及語言的本質之前，不要因此陷入虛無的自我懷疑。", "name": "普瑞賽斯"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_1718_1#1$1"}, {"id": 83, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "你可以理解為這裡是來自過去的一個瞬間，被我以資料的方式記錄。", "name": "普瑞賽斯"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_1718_1#1$1"}, {"id": 84, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "……但這段時光終究只是一幅靜滯的畫面，它永遠不會擁有未來。", "name": "普瑞賽斯"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_1718_1#1$1"}, {"id": 85, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "r", "name": "avg_npc_1719_1#2$1", "focus": "r"}}, {"id": 86, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "那您能否告訴我，為什麼我會出現在這裡？", "name": "希爾達"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_1719_1#2$1"}, {"id": 87, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "l", "name": "avg_npc_1718_1#1$1", "focus": "l"}}, {"id": 88, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "你死亡的那一剎那，我看見了你。", "name": "普瑞賽斯"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_1718_1#1$1"}, {"id": 89, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "有人驚擾了我，這是基於機率而發生的巧合。", "name": "普瑞賽斯"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_1718_1#1$1"}, {"id": 90, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "r", "name": "avg_npc_1719_1#3$1", "focus": "r"}}, {"id": 91, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "所以我，我……並不特殊。", "name": "希爾達"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_1719_1#3$1"}, {"id": 92, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "l", "name": "avg_npc_1718_1#8$1", "focus": "l"}}, {"id": 93, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "不，希爾達，你和你的同類很特殊。", "name": "普瑞賽斯"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_1718_1#8$1"}, {"id": 94, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "你們被源石塑造成了如今的模樣，與源石產生了如此奇妙的互動。", "name": "普瑞賽斯"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_1718_1#8$1"}, {"id": 95, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "你們的歷史、你們的文明，都是因源石而存在。", "name": "普瑞賽斯"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_1718_1#8$1"}, {"id": 96, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "r", "name": "avg_npc_1719_1#10$1", "focus": "r"}}, {"id": 97, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "但源石也帶來了許多痛苦，無盡的痛苦……", "name": "希爾達"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_1719_1#10$1"}, {"id": 98, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "l", "name": "avg_npc_1718_1#8$1", "focus": "l"}}, {"id": 99, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "是的，這是一個錯誤，你們的存在是計劃之外的狀況。", "name": "普瑞賽斯"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_1718_1#8$1"}, {"id": 100, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "r", "name": "avg_npc_1719_1#6$1", "focus": "r"}}, {"id": 101, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "什麼……", "name": "希爾達"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_1719_1#6$1"}, {"id": 102, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "您是說……泰拉上的人，都不應該活著嗎……", "name": "希爾達"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_1719_1#6$1"}, {"id": 103, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "l", "name": "avg_npc_1718_1#1$1", "focus": "l"}}, {"id": 104, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "不，你誤解了我的意思。", "name": "普瑞賽斯"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_1718_1#1$1"}, {"id": 105, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "你們的文明因機率而誕生，就像你會出現在這裡一樣，都是時間中客觀的存在。", "name": "普瑞賽斯"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_1718_1#1$1"}, {"id": 106, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "因機率而誕生，也因機率而消亡，這是這個宇宙中最普遍的規律。", "name": "普瑞賽斯"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_1718_1#1$1"}, {"id": 107, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "r", "name": "avg_npc_1719_1#10$1", "focus": "r"}}, {"id": 108, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "…………", "name": "希爾達"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_1719_1#10$1"}, {"id": 109, "prop": "dialog", "attributes": {}}, {"id": 110, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {}}, {"id": 111, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "卡特斯需要時間來消化這個事實。"}}, {"id": 112, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "為她帶來毀滅的源石，卻在這段靜滯的時間內給予了她安慰和取之不盡的知識。"}}, {"id": 113, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "她感到孤獨，卻並不痛苦。而更令她難受的是——"}}, {"id": 114, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "m", "name": "avg_npc_1719_1#10$1"}}, {"id": 115, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "泰拉……我的家鄉……", "name": "希爾達"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_1719_1#10$1"}, {"id": 116, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "並沒有被神明眷顧……", "name": "希爾達"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_1719_1#10$1"}, {"id": 117, "prop": "dialog", "attributes": {}}, {"id": 118, "prop": "Blocker", "attributes": {"a": 0.0, "r": 0.0, "g": 0.0, "b": 0.0, "fadetime": 0.0, "block": "true"}}, {"id": 119, "prop": "Blocker", "attributes": {"a": 1.0, "r": 0.0, "g": 0.0, "b": 0.0, "fadetime": 2.0, "block": "true"}}, {"id": 120, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {}}, {"id": 121, "prop": "Background", "attributes": {}}, {"id": 122, "prop": "Image", "attributes": {"image": "60_i08_1", "screenadapt": "coverall", "xScale": 1.05, "yScale": 1.05, "fadetime": 0.0}}, {"id": 123, "prop": "ImageTween", "attributes": {"xScaleFrom": 1.05, "yScaleFrom": 1.05, "xScaleTo": 1.0, "yScaleTo": 1.0, "duration": 20.0, "block": "false"}}, {"id": 124, "prop": "Blocker", "attributes": {"a": 0.0, "r": 0.0, "g": 0.0, "b": 0.0, "fadetime": 3.0, "block": "true"}}, {"id": 125, "prop": "Delay", "attributes": {"time": 1.0}}, {"id": 126, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "她回首看向了自己的身後。"}}, {"id": 127, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "無盡蔓延的大地，大地上起伏的漣漪如同一望無際的山丘。"}}, {"id": 128, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "她看不到終點，更看不到一絲泰拉的痕跡……"}}, {"id": 129, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "但卡特斯很清楚，那片大地一定就在她觸手可及的地方。"}}, {"id": 130, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "“泰拉”……", "name": "希爾達"}}, {"id": 131, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "一定會消亡嗎……", "name": "希爾達"}}, {"id": 132, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {}}, {"id": 133, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "那位背身仰望眼前巨構的“神明”並沒有回答她。"}}, {"id": 134, "prop": "dialog", "attributes": {}}, {"id": 135, "prop": "stopmusic", "attributes": {"fadetime": 2.0}}, {"id": 136, "prop": "Blocker", "attributes": {"a": 0.0, "r": 0.0, "g": 0.0, "b": 0.0, "fadetime": 0.0, "block": "true"}}, {"id": 137, "prop": "Blocker", "attributes": {"a": 1.0, "r": 0.0, "g": 0.0, "b": 0.0, "fadetime": 3.0, "block": "true"}}, {"id": 138, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {}}, {"id": 139, "prop": "image", "attributes": {}}, {"id": 140, "prop": "Delay", "attributes": {"time": 1.0}}, {"id": 141, "prop": "Subtitle", "attributes": {"text": "主教爺爺……", "x": 300.0, "y": 350.0, "alignment": "center", "size": 24.0, "delay": 0.04, "width": 700.0}}, {"id": 142, "prop": "Subtitle", "attributes": {"text": "您說的那個未來，真的存在嗎？", "x": 300.0, "y": 350.0, "alignment": "center", "size": 24.0, "delay": 0.04, "width": 700.0}}, {"id": 143, "prop": "subtitle", "attributes": {}}, {"id": 144, "prop": "Background", "attributes": {"image": "60_g10_rhodescorridor_origin", "screenadapt": "coverall"}}, {"id": 145, "prop": "Delay", "attributes": {"time": 1.0}}, {"id": 146, "prop": "PlaySound", "attributes": {"key": "$d_avg_energywell", "volume": 0.0, "loop": "true", "channel": "en"}}, {"id": 147, "prop": "SoundVolume", "attributes": {"volume": 0.4, "channel": "en", "fadetime": 2.0}}, {"id": 148, "prop": "PlaySound", "attributes": {"key": "$d_gen_surfacefrozen", "volume": 0.6, "loop": "true", "channel": "sur"}}, {"id": 149, "prop": "PlaySound", "attributes": {"key": "$d_avg_enemyappear_weird", "volume": 1.0}}, {"id": 150, "prop": "Blocker", "attributes": {"a": 0.0, "r": 0.0, "g": 0.0, "b": 0.0, "fadetime": 2.0, "block": "true"}}, {"id": 151, "prop": "Delay", "attributes": {"time": 1.0}}, {"id": 152, "prop": "StopSound", "attributes": {"channel": "sur", "fadetime": 3.0}}, {"id": 153, "prop": "CameraShake", "attributes": {"duration": 1.0, "xstrength": 20.0, "ystrength": 20.0, "vibrato": 30.0, "randomness": 90.0, "fadeout": "true", "block": "false"}}, {"id": 154, "prop": "Blocker", "attributes": {"a": 0.0, "r": 0.0, "g": 0.0, "b": 0.0, "fadetime": 0.0, "block": "true"}}, {"id": 155, "prop": "Blocker", "attributes": {"a": 1.0, "r": 1.0, "g": 1.0, "b": 1.0, "fadetime": 0.03, "block": "true"}}, {"id": 156, "prop": "PlaySound", "attributes": {"key": "$d_sp_amiyakilling", "volume": 1.0}}, {"id": 157, "prop": "Blocker", "attributes": {"a": 0.0, "r": 0.0, "g": 0.0, "b": 0.0, "fadetime": 1.0, "block": "true"}}, {"id": 158, "prop": "Delay", "attributes": {"time": 0.5}}, {"id": 159, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "m", "name": "avg_1037_amiya3_1#4$3"}}, {"id": 160, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "博士，小心！", "name": "阿米婭"}, "figure_art": "avg_1037_amiya3_1#4$3"}, {"id": 161, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "m", "name": "avg_1037_amiya3_1#6$3"}}, {"id": 162, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "這裡源石活性化的程度已經超過了凱爾希醫生的預期，源石結晶的生長速度非常驚人……", "name": "阿米婭"}, "figure_art": "avg_1037_amiya3_1#6$3"}, {"id": 163, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "還有那些源源不斷地出現的奇怪敵人——", "name": "阿米婭"}, "figure_art": "avg_1037_amiya3_1#6$3"}, {"id": 164, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {}}, {"id": 165, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "但你的注意力卻被眼前的源石所吸引。"}}, {"id": 166, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "每一個晶簇、每一個切面……"}}, {"id": 167, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "你都看到了同一個畫面——"}}, {"id": 168, "prop": "dialog", "attributes": {}}, {"id": 169, "prop": "Decision", "attributes": {"options": "我看到了……", "values": "1"}, "targetLine": {"option1": "line170"}}, {"id": 170, "prop": "Predicate", "attributes": {"references": "1"}, "endOfOpt": false}, {"id": 171, "prop": "Decision", "attributes": {"options": "她的背影在每一個切面出現。", "values": "1"}, "targetLine": {"option1": "line172"}}, {"id": 172, "prop": "Predicate", "attributes": {"references": "1"}, "endOfOpt": false}, {"id": 173, "prop": "Decision", "attributes": {"options": "還有一個人站在她的身邊？！", "values": "1"}, "targetLine": {"option1": "line174"}}, {"id": 174, "prop": "Predicate", "attributes": {"references": "1"}, "endOfOpt": false}, {"id": 175, "prop": "StopSound", "attributes": {"channel": "en", "fadetime": 2.0}}, {"id": 176, "prop": "Blocker", "attributes": {"a": 0.0, "r": 0.0, "g": 0.0, "b": 0.0, "fadetime": 0.0, "block": "true"}}, {"id": 177, "prop": "Blocker", "attributes": {"a": 1.0, "r": 0.0, "g": 0.0, "b": 0.0, "fadetime": 2.0, "block": "true"}}, {"id": 178, "prop": "Background", "attributes": {}}, {"id": 179, "prop": "playMusic", "attributes": {"intro": "$ghosthunter_intro", "key": "$ghosthunter_loop", "volume": 0.6}}, {"id": 180, "prop": "Image", "attributes": {"image": "60_i08_2", "screenadapt": "coverall", "xScale": 1.5, "yScale": 1.5, "y": 50.0}}, {"id": 181, "prop": "ImageTween", "attributes": {"duration": 20.0, "block": "false"}}, {"id": 182, "prop": "Blocker", "attributes": {"a": 0.0, "r": 0.0, "g": 0.0, "b": 0.0, "fadetime": 3.0, "block": "true"}}, {"id": 183, "prop": "Delay", "attributes": {"time": 1.0}}, {"id": 184, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "希爾達，你令我感到好奇。", "name": "普瑞賽斯"}}, {"id": 185, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "我在這裡可以觀察到你所在的世界的一切，你是這個文明中第二個與我交流的生命。", "name": "普瑞賽斯"}}, {"id": 186, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "我想問你……你依然愛著那片大地，對嗎？", "name": "普瑞賽斯"}}, {"id": 187, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "我想，是的……", "name": "希爾達"}}, {"id": 188, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "哪怕它帶給你們的痛苦也真實存在且揮之不去？", "name": "普瑞賽斯"}}, {"id": 189, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "是……", "name": "希爾達"}}, {"id": 190, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "你所在意的，也是如此嗎？", "name": "普瑞賽斯"}}, {"id": 191, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "呃……我不懂您的意思。", "name": "希爾達"}}, {"id": 192, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "只是對生命和意志的讚嘆。死亡沒有壓倒你。", "name": "普瑞賽斯"}}, {"id": 193, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "你為了求索一個關於未來的答案而尋找我，而我們現在已經站在答案之前——", "name": "普瑞賽斯"}}, {"id": 194, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "那是語言所無法描述的答案。", "name": "普瑞賽斯"}}, {"id": 195, "prop": "dialog", "attributes": {}}, {"id": 196, "prop": "Blocker", "attributes": {"a": 0.0, "r": 0.0, "g": 0.0, "b": 0.0, "fadetime": 0.0, "block": "true"}}, {"id": 197, "prop": "Blocker", "attributes": {"a": 1.0, "r": 0.0, "g": 0.0, "b": 0.0, "fadetime": 2.0, "block": "true"}}, {"id": 198, "prop": "image", "attributes": {}}, {"id": 199, "prop": "Background", "attributes": {"image": "60_g3_cvilizationtombstone", "screenadapt": "coverall"}}, {"id": 200, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "r", "name": "avg_npc_1719_1#1$1"}}, {"id": 201, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "l", "name": "avg_npc_1718_1#1$1"}}, {"id": 202, "prop": "Delay", "attributes": {"time": 1.0}}, {"id": 203, "prop": "Blocker", "attributes": {"a": 0.0, "r": 0.0, "g": 0.0, "b": 0.0, "fadetime": 2.0, "block": "true"}}, {"id": 204, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "r", "name": "avg_npc_1719_1#9$1", "focus": "r"}}, {"id": 205, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "——那是？！", "name": "希爾達"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_1719_1#9$1"}, {"id": 206, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "l", "name": "avg_npc_1718_1#1$1", "focus": "l"}}, {"id": 207, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "記得我剛剛提及的絕對存在的終極嗎？", "name": "普瑞賽斯"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_1718_1#1$1"}, {"id": 208, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "人們本以為那是一道遙遠星體燃燒時發出的光。", "name": "普瑞賽斯"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_1718_1#1$1"}, {"id": 209, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {}}, {"id": 210, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "卡特斯不自覺地抬起了頭，陰雲遮天蔽日，將黑暗送給了這片天地。"}}, {"id": 211, "prop": "dialog", "attributes": {}}, {"id": 212, "prop": "Blocker", "attributes": {"a": 0.0, "r": 0.0, "g": 0.0, "b": 0.0, "fadetime": 0.0, "block": "true"}}, {"id": 213, "prop": "Blocker", "attributes": {"a": 1.0, "r": 0.0, "g": 0.0, "b": 0.0, "fadetime": 2.0, "block": "true"}}, {"id": 214, "prop": "Background", "attributes": {}}, {"id": 215, "prop": "Delay", "attributes": {"time": 1.0}}, {"id": 216, "prop": "Image", "attributes": {"image": "60_i10_1", "screenadapt": "coverall"}}, {"id": 217, "prop": "ImageTween", "attributes": {"xFrom": 0.0, "xScaleFrom": 1.0, "yScaleFrom": 1.0, "xScaleTo": 1.3, "yScaleTo": 1.3, "duration": 60.0, "block": "false"}}, {"id": 218, "prop": "Blocker", "attributes": {"a": 0.0, "r": 0.0, "g": 0.0, "b": 0.0, "fadetime": 2.0, "block": "true"}}, {"id": 219, "prop": "Delay", "attributes": {"time": 1.0}}, {"id": 220, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "隨後，一絲微弱的光亮破開了一條烏雲的縫隙。人群仰望著那束光，讚嘆，驚呼。"}}, {"id": 221, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "而卡特斯似乎正完全身處人群之中。"}}, {"id": 222, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "我在親眼目睹——", "name": "希爾達"}}, {"id": 223, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "歷史。", "name": "普瑞賽斯"}}, {"id": 224, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "隨後，那束光在星球大氣的塵埃中散射出彩虹般的色彩，如同宇宙正在一塊黑色的畫布上塗抹顏色。"}}, {"id": 225, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "虔誠的生靈在他們的最後時刻，依舊在向著宇宙未知的賜福祈禱。", "name": "普瑞賽斯"}}, {"id": 226, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "而理性的科學主義者前赴後繼地乘坐著飛行器衝入光芒中，他們渴望近距離接觸真理。", "name": "普瑞賽斯"}}, {"id": 227, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "（……沒有任何動靜？為什麼他們衝入了光芒裡卻沒有任何動靜？）", "name": "希爾達"}}, {"id": 228, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "狂熱的唯心主義保守派憤怒地指責外來的敵人未經允許就進入了他們自意識誕生時就擁有的空間。", "name": "普瑞賽斯"}}, {"id": 229, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "他們毫無顧忌地將最危險的武器傾瀉向絢爛的天空。", "name": "普瑞賽斯"}}, {"id": 230, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "溫柔的光接納了一切，沒有爆炸，也沒有反擊。"}}, {"id": 231, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "光依舊沿著它既定的軌跡前進，完全無視了下方躁動的生靈，儘管混亂與死亡已經在他們之中滋生。"}}, {"id": 232, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "——這到底……發生了什麼？", "name": "希爾達"}}, {"id": 233, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "你想接近那束光嗎？", "name": "普瑞賽斯"}}, {"id": 234, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "……？！", "name": "希爾達"}}, {"id": 235, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "卡特斯感覺到了自己的視野在飛速地攀升，越過了騷亂的人群，越過了燃燒的山丘，越過了漆黑的雲層。"}}, {"id": 236, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "那些彩虹般的光，她觸手可及。"}}, {"id": 237, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "足以毀滅行星的武器從她的身邊飛過，沒入光中，悄無聲息；可以跨越星系的航船也紛紛墜向大地。"}}, {"id": 238, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "他們反抗。", "name": "普瑞賽斯"}}, {"id": 239, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "他們祈禱。", "name": "普瑞賽斯"}}, {"id": 240, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "他們試圖用千萬年來人為創造的一切美好說服那束冰冷的光——", "name": "普瑞賽斯"}}, {"id": 241, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "但那束光是如此冷漠，如深空一般冰冷。", "name": "普瑞賽斯"}}, {"id": 242, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "光掠過了星球，離開了。一切都安靜了下來。", "name": "普瑞賽斯"}}, {"id": 243, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "卡特斯發現自己的視野已經來到了深空之中，她正呆呆地凝望著那個破碎的天體……"}}, {"id": 244, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "一如她眺望幽靈時，她所好奇的，幽靈凝視的景象。"}}, {"id": 245, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "……毀滅……為什麼……", "name": "希爾達"}}, {"id": 246, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "毀滅從何而來？它為何而來？它離開了？它去了哪裡？還有那些生命呢——"}}, {"id": 247, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "她看到了。"}}, {"id": 248, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "當恆星的光芒再次照亮星球破碎的地表時，那裡只剩下無盡的殘骸。星體碎片正脫離引力的束縛，散向深空。"}}, {"id": 249, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "在那些碎片之上，也曾烙印著一個輝煌文明的印記。", "name": "普瑞賽斯"}}, {"id": 250, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "沒有人能在祂來臨之前做好準備。", "name": "普瑞賽斯"}}, {"id": 251, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "就連這個文明中最聰明、知識最淵博的智者也渴望在毀滅來臨之前得到一點預兆和警示。", "name": "普瑞賽斯"}}, {"id": 252, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "但很遺憾……", "name": "普瑞賽斯"}}, {"id": 253, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "卡特斯親眼目睹了神人們的死去，神人們的無能為力。她甚至短暫喪失了恐懼的本能。"}}, {"id": 254, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "這是……您所經歷的歷史？", "name": "希爾達"}}, {"id": 255, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "不，這只是我們捕獲到的萬千片段中的一個。", "name": "普瑞賽斯"}}, {"id": 256, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "我所親身經歷的，遠非這遠遠的一瞥可比。", "name": "普瑞賽斯"}}, {"id": 257, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "你所渴求的答案並未完全結束，你看，廢墟中就快出現聲音了。", "name": "普瑞賽斯"}}, {"id": 258, "prop": "dialog", "attributes": {}}, {"id": 259, "prop": "Image", "attributes": {"image": "60_i10_2", "screenadapt": "coverall", "fadetime": 3.0}}, {"id": 260, "prop": "ImageTween", "attributes": {"xScaleFrom": 1.0, "yScaleFrom": 1.0, "xScaleTo": 1.1, "yScaleTo": 1.1, "duration": 30.0, "block": "false"}}, {"id": 261, "prop": "delay", "attributes": {"time": 3.0}}, {"id": 262, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "那些從深空中到來的石頭——", "name": "希爾達"}}, {"id": 263, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "彗星。有時它們會帶來生命的種子。有時它們也僅僅只是填補那破碎的死寂行星。", "name": "普瑞賽斯"}}, {"id": 264, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "它們從哪裡來？", "name": "希爾達"}}, {"id": 265, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "任何地方。甚至恰好就來自另一個經歷了毀滅的行星，或許還刻印著那失落文明的痕跡。", "name": "普瑞賽斯"}}, {"id": 266, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "死去天體的引力開始捕獲更多來自深空的客人，它的身軀開始恢復。"}}, {"id": 267, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "……那些飄浮在深空中的艦船——", "name": "希爾達"}}, {"id": 268, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "來自他處的探索者、求知者、殖民者，抑或是純粹的掠奪者。", "name": "普瑞賽斯"}}, {"id": 269, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "他們同樣會加速文明演化的過程。", "name": "普瑞賽斯"}}, {"id": 270, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "您的意思是，“泰拉”……也有著同樣的經歷？", "name": "希爾達"}}, {"id": 271, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "你的貪婪壓過了你的恐懼。", "name": "普瑞賽斯"}}, {"id": 272, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "知識是不可逆轉的，希爾達。當你窺探到了片面的真理後，你是否還能安然地回到無知的黑暗中去呢？", "name": "普瑞賽斯"}}, {"id": 273, "prop": "dialog", "attributes": {}}, {"id": 274, "prop": "Blocker", "attributes": {"a": 0.0, "r": 0.0, "g": 0.0, "b": 0.0, "fadetime": 0.0, "block": "true"}}, {"id": 275, "prop": "Blocker", "attributes": {"a": 1.0, "r": 0.0, "g": 0.0, "b": 0.0, "fadetime": 2.0, "block": "true"}}, {"id": 276, "prop": "image", "attributes": {}}, {"id": 277, "prop": "Background", "attributes": {"image": "60_g3_cvilizationtombstone", "screenadapt": "coverall"}}, {"id": 278, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "r", "name": "avg_npc_1719_1#1$1"}}, {"id": 279, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "l", "name": "avg_npc_1718_1#1$1"}}, {"id": 280, "prop": "Delay", "attributes": {"time": 1.0}}, {"id": 281, "prop": "Blocker", "attributes": {"a": 0.0, "r": 0.0, "g": 0.0, "b": 0.0, "fadetime": 2.0, "block": "true"}}, {"id": 282, "prop": "Delay", "attributes": {"time": 1.0}}, {"id": 283, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "r", "focus": "n"}}, {"id": 284, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "卡特斯依然站在這個宏偉的“墓碑”之前。"}}, {"id": 285, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "她觸摸著其表面凸起的漣漪，渾身戰慄。"}}, {"id": 286, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "r", "name": "avg_npc_1719_1#1$1", "focus": "r"}}, {"id": 287, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "每一道痕跡，都意味著一個文明的終結……直到現在，我才更加有實感——", "name": "希爾達"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_1719_1#1$1"}, {"id": 288, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "r", "name": "avg_npc_1719_1#2$1", "focus": "r"}}, {"id": 289, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "我可以暫時留在這裡學習嗎？", "name": "希爾達"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_1719_1#2$1"}, {"id": 290, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "您讓我看到了通向答案的鑰匙，而所有的那些知識，需要我自己去理解。", "name": "希爾達"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_1719_1#2$1"}, {"id": 291, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "l", "name": "avg_npc_1718_1#2$1", "focus": "l"}}, {"id": 292, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "儘管這裡只是永恆靜止的時間碎片？", "name": "普瑞賽斯"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_1718_1#2$1"}, {"id": 293, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "r", "name": "avg_npc_1719_1#1$1", "focus": "r"}}, {"id": 294, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "……是。", "name": "希爾達"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_1719_1#1$1"}, {"id": 295, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "l", "name": "avg_npc_1718_1#1$1", "focus": "l"}}, {"id": 296, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "你們和我們很像。", "name": "普瑞賽斯"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_1718_1#1$1"}, {"id": 297, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "你可以自由地行走在這裡和羅德島上的任何地方，去理解你想要的答案。", "name": "普瑞賽斯"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_1718_1#1$1"}, {"id": 298, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "至於以後，留在這裡，或是回到你牽掛的泰拉……", "name": "普瑞賽斯"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_1718_1#1$1"}, {"id": 299, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "我會尊重你的選擇。我們很快會再見面的。", "name": "普瑞賽斯"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_1718_1#1$1"}, {"id": 300, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "r", "name": "avg_npc_1719_1#9$1", "focus": "r"}}, {"id": 301, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "您、您要離開……您要去哪裡？", "name": "希爾達"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_1719_1#9$1"}, {"id": 302, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "l", "name": "avg_npc_1718_1#8$1", "focus": "l"}}, {"id": 303, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "有人在等我。", "name": "普瑞賽斯"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_1718_1#8$1"}, {"id": 304, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "……已經等了太久太久。", "name": "普瑞賽斯"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_1718_1#8$1"}, {"id": 305, "prop": "dialog", "attributes": {}}, {"id": 306, "prop": "stopmusic", "attributes": {"fadetime": 2.0}}, {"id": 307, "prop": "Blocker", "attributes": {"a": 0.0, "r": 0.0, "g": 0.0, "b": 0.0, "fadetime": 0.0, "block": "true"}}, {"id": 308, "prop": "Blocker", "attributes": {"a": 1.0, "r": 0.0, "g": 0.0, "b": 0.0, "fadetime": 3.0, "block": "true"}}, {"id": 309, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {}}, {"id": 310, "prop": "PlayMusic", "attributes": {"intro": "$darkness01_intro", "key": "$darkness01_loop", "volume": 0.6}}, {"id": 311, "prop": "Background", "attributes": {"image": "60_g4_rhodesabyss_w", "screenadapt": "coverall"}}, {"id": 312, "prop": "focusout", "attributes": {"type": "bg", "id": "60_g4_rhodesabyss_w", "from": 0.0, "to": 1.0, "duration": 0.1, "block": "false"}}, {"id": 313, "prop": "PlaySound", "attributes": {"key": "$d_avg_labamb", "volume": 1.0, "loop": "true", "channel": "a"}}, {"id": 314, "prop": "Delay", "attributes": {"time": 2.0}}, {"id": 315, "prop": "Blocker", "attributes": {"a": 0.6, "r": 0.0, "g": 0.0, "b": 0.0, "fadetime": 2.0, "block": "true"}}, {"id": 316, "prop": "Sticker", "attributes": {"id": "st1", "multi": "true", "text": "非法第三方嵌入程式已強制刪除，已恢復至初始設定。", "x": 180.0, "y": 170.0, "alignment": "left", "size": 24.0, "delay": 0.04, "width": 700.0, "block": "true"}}, {"id": 317, "prop": "Sticker", "attributes": {"id": "st1", "multi": "true", "t